le path up to Thomas Jefferson’s estate; while a strict leash law is enforced here to protect the sensitive landscape, it remains a premier destination for leashed forest hikes. Local favorites like King Family Vineyards even welcome four-legged fans to their weekly polo matches, creating a sophisticated social atmosphere for pets. Navigating the city’s requirements is made easy with a unique lifetime dog license available for a one-time $10 fee, provided rabies vaccinations remain current. For those looking to invest in this thriving pet market, our \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"4\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/owner-resources\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"owner resources\\\"}],null,\\\" offer critical data on development and zoning. From the \\\\\\\"Paws and Pints\\\\\\\" culture at local breweries to the quiet beauty of the Blue Ridge, Charlottesville remains an elite destination for Virginia’s active canine companions.\\\"]}]]}],\\\"$L31\\\",\\\"$L32\\\"]}],\\\"$L33\\\"]}]}],\\\"$L34\\\",\\\"$L35\\\",\\\"$L36\\\",\\\"$L37\\\",\\\"$L38\\\",\\\"$L39\\\",\\\"$L3a\\\",\\\"$L3b\\\",\\\"$L3c\\\",\\\"$L3d\\\",\\\"$L3e\\\",\\\"$L3f\\\"]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"2b:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"footer\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-new\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-container\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-grid\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-column\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h4\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-heading\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"IndoorDogPark\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"ul\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-links\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/about\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"About