e\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/fluffy-s-pet-shop\",\"name\":\"Fluffy's Pet Shop\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/fluffy-s-pet-shop\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Fluffy's Pet Shop.  What makes this dog facility special is its attentive, knowledgeable, clean. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Charlottesville\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":8,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/flydog-yoga\",\"name\":\"FlyDog Yoga\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/flydog-yoga\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about FlyDog Yoga.  What makes this dog facility special is its safe, convenient, attentive. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Charlottesville\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":9,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/atlantic-coast-k-9-training-service\",\"name\":\"Atlantic Coast K-9 Training Service\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/atlantic-coast-k-9-training-service\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Atlantic Coast K-9 Training Service.  What makes this dog facility special is its friendly, caring, convenient. The staff's dedication to creating a positive...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Charlottesville\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":10,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/crate-marrow\",\"name\":\"Crate & Marrow\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpar